    <tags>rdp remote-desktop electron react desktop</tags>
    <summary>Lightweight RDP Remote Desktop Client</summary>
    <description>
A fast, modern Remote Desktop Protocol (RDP) client built with Electron, React, and TailwindCSS. 

## Features
- Encrypted Storage - All connections and credentials are encrypted with AES-256-GCM
- Multiple Connections - Save and organize unlimited RDP connections
- Independently Pinnable Windows - Each connection opens in its own window
- Dynamic Resizing - Session windows resize dynamically
- Native RDP Protocol - Pure TypeScript RDP implementation
- Full Audio Support - RDPSND virtual channel with Web Audio API
- Modern UI - Dark theme, glass morphism, smooth animations
- NLA/TLS Security - NTLMv2 authentication via CredSSP
- Clipboard Support - Clipboard virtual channel for copy/paste
    </description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/bluewhackadoo/RDPea/releases/tag/v1.0.4</releaseNotes>
